neuros (1.0.0) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of NeurOS — Ubuntu 24.04 LTS with local LLM integration.
  * Core tools: nn (terminal assistant), neuros-tray, neuros-welcome
  * Build system: live-build configs, hooks, package lists
  * AI features: neuros-chat (web GUI), neuros-model (model manager)
  * Dev tools: neuros-git (AI git assistant), neuros-snippets (code manager)
  * System: neuros-agent (context agent), neuros-mcp (MCP server)
  * Voice: neuros-voice (STT), neuros-speak (TTS)
  * Privacy: No telemetry, UFW firewall, local-only AI
  * Desktop: GNOME 46 dark theme, dash-to-dock, zsh, neovim

 -- NeurOS Team <dev@neuros.local>  Mon, 22 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000
